Every time a block type is mined for the first time, the person who mined it will receive a reward (default is gold ingot).

Commands:
Operators only:
/blockrush enable/on/true/start   - Enables the scenario and resets the list of blocks which have already been mined
/blockrush disable/off/false/stop - Disables the scenario
/blockrush reset                  - Resets the list of blocks which have already been mined
/blockrush setreward              - Sets the reward to the item you're currently holding
Everyone:
/blockrush list                   - Lists the blocks which have already been mined
/blockrush reward                 - Tells you what the reward is for mining a new block type
/blockrush help                   - Gives you a list of the commands
